independent_claims.raw_text:
A portable solar charger comprising:
 a plurality of photovoltaic panels configured to convert solar radiation into direct current electrical power;
 a folding mechanism connecting said photovoltaic panels, wherein said folding mechanism enables the panels to transition between a compact folded configuration and an expanded deployed configuration;
 a maximum power point tracking charge controller electrically connected to said photovoltaic panels;
 a rechargeable lithium-ion battery electrically connected to said charge controller;
 a USB Type-C output port configured to provide regulated power to an external electronic device.

